criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Acute leukemia patients (including AML and ANML) at first complete remission before transplantation;
2. HLA matching of the donor and the patients was haploidentical;
3. Patients recieved allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation in our hospital from January 2016 to   
December 2019.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Patients aged 14~55 years old;
2. Patients don't achieve remission;
3. Patients with heart,lung or kidney dysfunction;
4. Patients with mental disorders;
5. Pregnancy patients with leukemia.
